quoted_tweet.text:
gm rwa researchers,

25,000+

that's how many companies Computershare manages shareholder records for

and they could all be coming onchain after Computershare partners with @Securitize

let’s dive into the details

----------------------------------------------------------

1. Top News:

@Securitize partners @Computershare to enable U.S. companies to issue tokenized equity alongside traditional shares.
→ https://t.co/CAnnHQJ8wx

@NYSE proposes rule change for tokenized equities and ETFs trading with T+1 settlement under DTC pilot.
→ https://t.co/uZ3IZKF2YL

2. Tokenized Securities Round-Up:

@OndoFinance partners Broadridge to enable governance across 250+ tokenized stocks and ETFs while expanding distribution via Kucoin Wallet.
→ https://t.co/ZOX3OpadMj
→ https://t.co/gi80C1B2kV

@xStocksFi expands to BNB via PancakeSwap and integrates with @coinroutes for institutional trading.
→ https://t.co/k00cFR9JZO
→ https://t.co/F0RIhUwEsM

@elementaldefi launches ONyc V2 vault with 20.04% APY.
→ https://t.co/9hEd2TnEII

@centrifuge expands to Monad with TBILLs and launches deSPX infra via broader integrations.
→ https://t.co/ZIzufmnoKV

@CtrlAltCo launches first tokenized structured product on Solana.
→ https://t.co/nHinAlstj4

PreStocks expands distribution via Avici.
→ https://t.co/zhizgkkLJT

@AssetoFinance partners @KeyringNetwork to bring leveraged access to RWAs via rwa [un]wind protocol.
→ https://t.co/GyLW0ofFme

@humafinance selects Chainlink CCIP as crosschain bridge for PST and future products.
→ https://t.co/hf3KTnYqOV

@dflow goes live on @Tessera_PE.
→ https://t.co/uTaC6lwlpP

@agamafinance partners @FatraLabs to build liquidity infrastructure for tokenized private credit across GCC markets.
→ https://t.co/aJXWPz3Jdy

@coinbase launches CUSHY, a tokenized credit fund on Base managed by Northern Trust and @SuperstateInc.
→ https://t.co/kwvEW5sqge

3. RWA Stablecoins Round-Up:

@OpenEden_X expands into derivatives infra via STS Digital partnership while launching PRISM vault on Upshift.
→ https://t.co/M0eNPHwMq3
→ https://t.co/oAcHyZ9RBZ

@flowdesk_co raises sUSDai borrow cap to $250M on Morpho.
→ https://t.co/HUiNu9WVg3

@Theo_Network opens $thUSD access to public following Genesis program.
→ https://t.co/vnBeOVXITL

@roycoprotocol partners @Raacfi to use pmUSD as credit for its Senior Vault.
→ https://t.co/ttUuhQni8C

4. Other News:

@MANTRA_Chain expands into commodities via Cropto for tokenized agricultural assets while launching its first LST for $MANTRA via @FluxtraMANTRA.
→ https://t.co/drfecauZ2v
→ https://t.co/9x44xjzqd5

@streamex distributes first gold yield at 3.5% APY.
→ https://t.co/wRbjDwm641

@Collector_Crypt partners @Loopscale preparing to enable USDC borrowing against trading cards.
→ https://t.co/E0J0gR7NHw

@DigiFTTech and Flow Capital launch $150M APAC credit fund token ($FLOWC).
→ https://t.co/YT5VEt4vWd

@integra_layer testnet goes live.
→ https://t.co/iIbAEpoGgh

@tradexyz launches Pre-IPO perpetuals.
→ https://t.co/Gf0krGjj5M

@RealFinOfficial lists $ASSET across OKX, Kucoin, MEXC, and Kraken.
→ https://t.co/Av6lexkKOO

@Brickken partners @ADIChain_  to deploy tokenization infra across MENA.
→ https://t.co/pN1HaQtOCC

@KAIO_xyz announces upcoming token $KAIO launch.
→ https://t.co/3bhXZVXueI

@NUVAFinance raises $5.2M from Morgan Creek.
→ https://t.co/2CI0KAsePU

@MidasRWA partners Symbiotic for instant liquidity within its architecture.
→ https://t.co/utih75xWy6

----------------------------------------------------------

that's it for this week's RWA recap

if you want a shorter daily version, join my TG channel, link in bio

this also marks the 20th edition of the recap, so i made a new banner for it

let me know what you think, should i keep it?

